{"tid":2306254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭自爆生活只有工作 無時間與丈夫聊天","createTime":"2020-11-30T09:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T11:01:07.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff09ed2eecdbb6aba54d82b0a6bcacc00618fce","tid":2306254,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥早前接受《南華早報》專訪，提及自己現時生活只有工作，沒有消閒活動，她也沒花時間和丈夫林兆波聊天。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在訪問中表示，自己把每一分鐘的時間都放在工作上，真的有很多工作要為香港而做，又稱「除了工作，我都不做其他事情」，「我甚至沒有花時間跟我丈夫聊天溝通，這確實是工作狂的生活」。<br />\n<br />\n被問及是否從工作當中獲得娛樂，林鄭表示「當然，有大有小」，並指自己工作的最大樂趣不是來自大政策如建屋等，而是做一些相對細微的政策，例如幫助罕見病人獲得藥物，支援基層家庭生活需要如提供電腦等，但她補充，自己不會為了幫助小眾而忽略制訂大方向政策。<br />\n<br />\n而當被問到家人如何應對自己所承受自己的壓力時，林鄭就指「我只能說我的家人完全支持我」，「除此之外，我不想再講詳情了。」"},{"pid":"725e510cf5890a078c2ec888a2e18dcecc2df443","tid":2306254,"uid":10438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"都無咩好講了"},{"pid":"b43c56dd4cc930ac9137ec92d088d9c4555f16f8","tid":2306254,"uid":151321,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"冇提仔女？"},{"pid":"929cab1d965af36d6ebe8ddebe67c3fc0388658b","tid":2306254,"uid":61115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"仲聊天?<br />\n一埋位就 屌你老母 啦"},{"pid":"4e02128b7d5aec15ca3245c38f925526591aca61","tid":2306254,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"工作狂<br />\n上到去咪又係要搖頭擺尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9cdad0acd2d2fe68befade358703a624ec0fac","tid":2306254,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:06:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cef1a84a17104aba17366308c45ddc1c02eeb31","tid":2306254,"uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"好懷疑佢啲娛樂係睇到後生仔被打到爆頭同入罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64568073b0c2075a274b4f8cbf861e889db47bf","tid":2306254,"uid":216228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},{"pid":"1e01004ad91d95a6c9d54d4bd053a37cb9722011","tid":2306254,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"其實做唔掂真係唔好勉強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34e1862bc212d5fa93a691c5ac46bd30630dd61","tid":2306254,"uid":121270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"香港支化就係佢最大娛樂"},{"pid":"0f4e79cda7ca67cdd1aef3fe824b8a4f637b2d07","tid":2306254,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"有冇做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b042133d4e8efdfbba53ed03e1c3e8117eb43a84","tid":2306254,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"玩9你班仆街咪樂趣lo"},{"pid":"1d297b53d745f40961a31c30deb9aa3ed464c89c","tid":2306254,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f4e79cda7ca67cdd1aef3fe824b8a4f637b2d07","tid":2306254,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"有冇做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"林太太的五十道陰影"},{"pid":"fd657a1eab596b70c76430347de7f8a579599548","tid":2306254,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"習近平唔屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20cd03266ada3014af2d5b8e68e06ccfa96a356","tid":2306254,"uid":284575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d297b53d745f40961a31c30deb9aa3ed464c89c","tid":2306254,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f4e79cda7ca67cdd1aef3fe824b8a4f637b2d07","tid":2306254,"uid":13